text: Tumacya striyampaiki jya striya masika palibabata nirasa jhalya asatila, jara tumhala sanka asela tara tyanci iddata tina mahine ahe, ani tyancidekhila, jyanna ajuna masika pali suru jhaleli nasela, ani garbhavati striyanci iddata tyanci prastuti hone ahe ani jo manusya allahace bhaya balagela, allaha tyacya pratyeka kamata sahajata nirmana karila
